        ("What are common things a dentist checks?",["teeth","gums","cavity","x ray","bite","clean","check","look","health"],"Name two things","They usually check for cavities and clean my teeth and look at my gums","think"),
        ("How do you feel about going to the dentist?",["nervous","okay","fine","scared","anxious","not bad","okay with it","little worried"],"Say how you feel","I feel a little nervous but I know it is important for my health","nod"),
