        ("They tell you to avoid certain foods for a few hours. What do you ask?",["which foods","what not to eat","hot cold","restrictions","avoid","careful","eat","drink"],"Ask what to avoid","Which foods or drinks should I avoid and for how long","think"),
        ("They say avoid hot food for two hours. What do you say?",["okay","got it","understood","will do","two hours","sure","alright","no hot food"],"Confirm","Okay I will avoid hot food for two hours I understand","nod"),
