        ("They say they will be gentle. How do you respond?",["thank you","appreciate","feel better","helps","okay","good to know","relieved","glad"],"Say thank you","Thank you that helps a lot I feel a little better now","nod"),
        ("You ask them to stop if you raise your hand. What do you say?",["raise hand","signal","stop","need break","pause","tell you","give sign","uncomfortable"],"Ask for a signal","Could we agree that if I raise my hand you will pause for a moment","think"),
