        ("They say to rinse with mouthwash. Do you have any questions?",["when to rinse","which type","before after","morning night","how long","which one","type"],"Ask a question","Should I use mouthwash before or after brushing and is there a specific type","think"),
        ("They explain and you are ready to go. What do you say?",["thank you","got it","understood","really helpful","will do","try that","appreciate","good advice"],"Close the visit","Thank you that was really helpful I will definitely follow those tips goodbye","wave"),
