        ("Nurse asks how your teeth have been. What do you say?",["fine","one spot","sensitive","little pain","bothering me","okay except","noticed","mostly good"],"Describe your experience","Mostly fine but I have noticed one sensitive spot on my lower right side","sad"),
        ("Dentist says they will check it. You feel nervous. What do you say?",["little nervous","scared","anxious","will it hurt","does it","okay but","nervous about"],"Say how you feel","I am a little nervous could you tell me what to expect","think"),
        ("Dentist says it is routine. How do you respond?",["okay","good to know","feel better","thank you","relieved","appreciate","glad"],"Express relief","Okay good to know that makes me feel better thank you","nod"),
